#
Start w/ no Certs, Provisions or App Id
Clone snowlake

Open . -> select snowflake.xcodeproj

Left pane (far left icon select above) -> click 'snowflake', center Project -> snowflake, right pane
-> Indentity and Type -> change name -> enter

Popup -> rename all

Left pane ->  (far left icon select above) -> click 'fireball' ->
center -> Target -> fireball -> top -> "General" -> center -> Identity
-> Bundle Identifier -> 'org.bartonhammond.fireball'

Xcode -> Top row -> run icon has 'showflake', select it, -> "Manage
Scheme" -> select 'snowflake' and click the name to change it to ->
fireball

Xcode -> left pane under Fireball, select folder snowflake, far right
pane -> Identity and Type -> change to 'fireball'

Connect device to Mac

Select device in Xcode top row

Xcode -> Run
